\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa120 5.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa120\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang1038\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038\i0\b0 Hogyan \'edrn\'e1 le a k\'f6nyve tartalm\'e1t r\'f6viden (2-3 sorban)?\line }
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa120 6.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa120\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang1038\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038\i0\b0 Szeretn\'e9-e, ha az Ad Librum lenne a k\'f6nyv kiad\'f3ja? \line }
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa120 7.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa120\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang1038\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038\i0\b0 Mit gondol, a c\'e9lk\'f6z\'f6ns\'e9g\'e9t hogyan tudn\'e1 \'d6n (a saj\'e1t tev\'e9kenys\'e9g\'e9vel) a lehet\u337\'3f legjobban el\'e9rni?\line }
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa120 8.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa120\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang1038\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038\i0\b0 Honnan szerzett tudom\'e1st a kiad\'e1si programunkr\'f3l? (Ismer\u337\'3fst\u337\'3fl, internetes keres\u337\'3fb\u337\'3fl, internetes hirdet\'e9sb\u337\'3fl stb.)\line }
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa120 9.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa120\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang1038\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038\i0\b0 Ha szeretne az Ad Librum nyomtatott katal\'f3gus\'e1b\'f3l egy p\'e9ld\'e1nyt, sz\'edveskedj\'e9k ide\'edrni a postac\'edm\'e9t!\line }
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa120 10.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa120\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang1038\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang1038\i0\b0 Ha b\'e1rmilyen egy\'e9b megjegyz\'e9se, hozz\'e1f\u369\'3fznival\'f3ja van, k\'e9rj\'fck, \'edrja ide!\line }
